THUNDER LIZARD DRAGON

The Thunder Lizard Dragon is a massive, electricity-wielding dragon race.
While not quite as powerful as the Great Horned Dragon, it brings enormous
physical capability, lightning breath, and complete immunity to electricity
to the table.  It is the most "primal" of the playable dragons: a creature
of raw elemental power rather than arcane subtlety.

ATTRIBUTES (approximate ranges):
  IQ: 11-26  ME: 11-26  MA: 9-24   PS: 26-56 (Supernatural)
  PP: 7-22   PE: 25-50  PB: 2-12   Spd: 12-32

DAMAGE POOL:
  MDC: 5d6 x10 + 80 (approx 130-380 MDC)
  HP: PE + 2d6

SPECIAL ABILITIES:
  - MDC body: immune to SDC/HP weapons
  - Supernatural Physical Strength and Endurance
  - Lightning breath weapon
  - Complete immunity to electricity
  - Natural flight
  - Nightvision 300 ft
  - Sense Rifts and ley lines

PENALTIES:
  - Not OCC eligible
  - Dragon-sized: cannot enter most buildings
  - Hunted by Coalition and dragon hunters

OCC ELIGIBLE: No.
ALIGNMENT: Any.

